defeat you at the end!

7
00:00:48,169 --> 00:00:50,729
Are your plans for world domination
going well?

8
00:00:51,105 --> 00:00:52,072
Oh, Johan!

9
00:00:52,640 --> 00:00:54,665
He's not falling over at all!

10
00:00:56,044 --> 00:00:59,503
Things will be rough after you
take over the world.

11
00:01:00,682 --> 00:01:02,548
What kind of world are you
going to make?

12
00:01:03,051 --> 00:01:06,749
I don't care.
I'm finished after I mess it up!

13
00:01:07,188 --> 00:01:11,147
What?! It sounds like more fun
to mess it up.

14
00:01:11,426 --> 00:01:14,885
I'll quit the Rainbow Rangers
and join the evil organization!

15
00:01:19,267 --> 00:01:21,634
Now then, shall we start
heading back?

16
00:01:22,337 --> 00:01:23,304
Okay.

17
00:01:23,371 --> 00:01:25,703
All right, let's all head back.
Don't forget anything.

18
