31
00:04:11,906 --> 00:04:12,873
Oh yeah.

32
00:04:13,875 --> 00:04:16,970
Show her this when
you think it's appropriate.

33
00:04:18,146 --> 00:04:22,447
They're newspaper clippings
and a copy of the report

34
00:04:22,517 --> 00:04:25,043
from when I shot
that young serial killer.

35
00:04:30,658 --> 00:04:33,457
I'm not going to ask you to explain.

36
00:04:34,529 --> 00:04:38,864
The truth is that I killed someone.
I'm not justifying my actions.

37
00:04:40,168 --> 00:04:44,036
It's just that I want her
to know the truth.

38
00:04:47,208 --> 00:04:48,175
I understand.

39
00:04:54,615 --> 00:04:56,344
When...can I meet her?

40
00:04:58,319 --> 00:05:03,155
I'll ask her once more
if she wants to meet her father.

41
00:05:04,659 --> 00:05:09,825
I-I see ! I'll be waiting for a call !
I return home every night at 9:00!

42
00:05:09,997 --> 00:05:13,126
Richard, you're back
to your old self again.

43
00:05:14,168 --> 00:05:14,794
Huh?

44
00:05:15,036 --> 00:05:19,735
You have the same look in your eyes
as when you were younger...

45
00:05:19,807 --> 00:05:23,539
When you first became
a detective... When we first met.

46
00:05:29,450 --> 00:05:30,383
I see.

47
00:05:32,420 --> 00:05:36,584
What do you think? You'll get a bonus
if you sign up now.

48
00:05:37,325 --> 00:05:41,228
